WEBVTT

00:00:00.756 --> 00:00:02.716
Zdravo, kako ste?

00:00:02.716 --> 00:00:04.596
(Uzvici)

00:00:04.636 --> 00:00:06.476
Spremni da rešite 
klimatske promene?

00:00:06.516 --> 00:00:07.636
(Uzvici)

00:00:07.676 --> 00:00:09.076
Super.

00:00:09.116 --> 00:00:11.156
Znate li šta je petavat čas?

00:00:11.916 --> 00:00:16.716
To je jedinica za energiju,
poput kilovat časa ili megavat časa.

00:00:17.236 --> 00:00:19.436
Ja sam klimatski aktivista od 11. godine

00:00:19.476 --> 00:00:20.956
i studirao sam inženjerstvo,

00:00:20.996 --> 00:00:23.236
pa su mi te reči bile poznate.

00:00:23.276 --> 00:00:27.236
Kilovat, megavat,
pa i gigavat i teravat.

00:00:27.596 --> 00:00:29.636
Ali nikada nisam čuo za petavat čas

00:00:29.636 --> 00:00:32.356
dok nisam napisao knjigu
o rešenjima za klimatske promene.